@base = http://localhost:7331

### Ping — confirm the service is up and see the panel path
GET {{base}}/api/ping

### List events — each call appears in the panel's Requests tab
GET {{base}}/api/events

### Create an event — also logged via panel.Logger(), visible in Logs tab
POST {{base}}/api/events
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "My first panel event"
}

### Open the DevPanel in your browser:
### http://localhost:7331/keel/panel
###
### Tabs available:
###   /keel/panel/requests  — captured HTTP requests with latency
###   /keel/panel/logs      — structured logs from panel.Logger()
###   /keel/panel/routes    — all registered routes
###   /keel/panel/addons    — registered Debuggable addons
###   /keel/panel/config    — resolved application.properties values
